<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.1">
<l>māṇikkaṅ kaṭṭi vayira miṭaikaṭṭi</l>
<l>yāṇippoṉ ṉāṟceyta vaṇṇac ciṟuttoṭṭil</l>
<l>pēṇi yuṉakkup piramaṉ viṭutantāṉ</l>
<l>māṇik kuṟaḷaṉē tālēlō vaiyamaḷa ntāṉē tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Brahmā tenderly sent to you a small, coloured cradle that was made with</l>
<l>superior gold, adorned with rubies [and] closely set with diamonds.</l>
<l>You who are the brahmacārin Dwarf, tālēlō!</l>
<l>You who measured the earth, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
